lead_paragraph: Nancy Walton had career highs of 14 points, nine rebounds and seven blocks and No. 24 Oklahoma won its 12th-straight Big 12 Conference opener 84-54 over Kansas on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 24 Oklahoma Women Beat Kansas 84-54 in Big 12 Opener
